## 🔒 SECURITY RULES

- Never store raw IP addresses — always hash with `crypto.createHash('sha256')`
- Never expose stack traces or internal errors to the client in production
- Never commit `.env` files — they are in `.gitignore`
- Never put secrets in client-side code — only `VITE_` prefixed public vars allowed
- Always apply rate limiting on contact form (5 per hour) and general API (100 per 15 min)
- Always validate with Zod before any database operation
- Helmet is always active — never disable it

