## ♿ ACCESSIBILITY RULES

Every component must:
- Be reachable via `Tab` key
- Have a visible `:focus-visible` style (neon cyan outline)
- Have `aria-label` if icon-only or purpose is not obvious from text
- Use semantic HTML (`<button>` not `<div onClick>`)
- Respect `prefers-reduced-motion` (wrap all GSAP animations in the check)
- Use correct heading hierarchy (h1 → h2 → h3 → h4, never skip levels)

External links must always have:
```tsx
target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
```

