## 🌿 GIT RULES

### Branch Strategy
```
main              ← production only
dev               ← integration branch, always deployable
feature/phase-X   ← one branch per phase
fix/issue-name    ← bug fixes only
```

### Commit Message Format
```
type(scope): short description in present tense

feat(hero): add particle field mouse interaction
fix(contact): resolve form validation edge case
style(globals): update cyan glow intensity
chore(deps): install framer-motion
docs(roadmap): mark phase 2 complete
refactor(projects): extract card tilt logic to hook
```

Types: `feat` | `fix` | `style` | `refactor` | `chore` | `docs` | `test`

### Never commit:
- `.env` files
- `node_modules/`
- `dist/`
- `.DS_Store`
- Any file with hardcoded secrets

